\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 19. D. gredinii} Elis. Ekman,{\i  Svensk Bot. Tidskr.}{\b  27}: 102 (1933). Like {\b 18} but leaves usually sparsely hairy and often denticulate; petals pale yellow.{\i  Spitsbergen.} Sb. ({\i Greenland}.)
\par

